msgid "This screen provides the basic settings for configuring AutoClose."
msgstr ""

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:595
msgid "Enable the scheduler option to autoclose comments and/or pingbacks/trackbacks as per the options set in the Comments and Pingbacks/Trackbacks tabs."
msgstr ""

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:600
msgid "This screen provides settings to automatically close comments."
msgstr ""

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:601
msgid "Enable the Close comments option to close comments on posts as per the schedule in the General tab. You can select the post types on which you want to close comments and the age of the post in days."
msgstr ""

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:602
msgid "If you want to keep comments on certain posts open, enter a comma-separated list of post IDs in the field provided."
msgstr ""

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:607
msgid "This screen provides settings to automatically close pingbacks and trackbacks."
msgstr ""

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:608
msgid "Enable the Close pingbacks/trackbacks option to close pingbacks and trackbacks on posts as per the schedule in the General tab. You can select the post types on which you want to close pingbacks/trackbacks and the age of the post in days."
msgstr ""

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:609
msgid "If you want to keep pingbacks/trackbacks on certain posts open, enter a comma-separated list of post IDs in the field provided."
msgstr ""

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:610
msgid "Additionally, you can choose to delete all pingbacks and trackbacks when the scheduled maintenance runs."
msgstr ""

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:615
msgid "This screen provides settings to automatically delete post revisions."
msgstr ""

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:616
msgid "Enable the Delete post revisions option to delete post revisions when the scheduled maintenance runs."
msgstr ""

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:617
msgid "You can also set the number of revisions to keep for each post type. Set to 0 to delete all revisions."
msgstr ""

